column5: Colin Mochrie and Brad Sherwood (Whose Line Is It Anyway) take improv to the very painful next level at the 2005 Just For Laughs.  500 set traps + 2 blindfolds + 4 bare feet = 1 extremely funny video  Their "Shakespeare scene" is also quite good.  Best pun on 'voulez-vous coucher avec moi' I've ever heard.
